Article 6 (Formulation and Implementation of Annual Action Plan)
* The Minister of the Korea Forest Service shall annually formulate and implement an action plan
* A detailed implementation plan for managing and improving domestic and overseas carbon sinks;
* Legal or institutional improvements with regard to carbon sinks;
* Other matters necessary for managing and improving carbon sinks in the corresponding year.
* The procedures and methods for formulating the action plan shall be prescribed by Presidential Decree.
* The Board on Improvement of Carbon Sinks shall be established under the Korea Forest Service to
