Article 8 (Compilation of Information and Statistics on Carbon Sinks)
* The Minister of the Korea Forest Service shall compile information and statistics on the following with
* Outcomes from performing afforestation or similar activities under Article 9;
* Outcomes from performing forest management in the protected zone under Article 10;
* Status on the distribution and use of harvested wood products under Article 13;
* Information on energy in the timber industry under Article 14;
* Outcomes from utilizing forest biomass energy under Article 15;
* Outcomes from preventing deforestation and forest degradation under Article 16;
